{
  "stem": "6526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There in Majdanek, they gave us on a metal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We wore it on the hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On a metal, it had the number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we went out to work on the-- on the fields, dig ditches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What these ditches were for I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we dig-- we did dig ditches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in, in the-- in the bunk-- in the bunks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to have 8 to 10 and they were lined at three levels-- three levels.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a matter of fact, I think in, in Majdanek, we had different beds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had different beds in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had bunks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in another place, we had different-- in Birkenau, we also had bunks-- 8, 10, or maybe more on, on one level, but three levels.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were, because it came later-- it came later on after I, I came in the-- in May 8th or 10th to Majdanek, it came later-- other came transports.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whether they-- whether I came with a transport, although I came at certain time, it was before the other ones were on Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I may came later, but there, there were people there before me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't take them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know who came-- who went out of the-- of the Warsaw Ghetto before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew what the outcome was, that there were another few week or two.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a lot of butchering, a lot of killings.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
